---
title: Peach and Mozzarella Flatbread with Walnuts and Balsamic-Arugula Salad
description: Behold the ultimate summertime flatbread! Salty mozzarella and juicy peaches offer a delicious sweet-and-salty contrast. Peppery arugula is the cherry on top!
